        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Fauci's Incompetence Requires Early Dismissal Act or the FIRED Act</strong></p> <p>This bill retroactively prohibits an individual from serving as the Director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases for more than 12 years.</p>]]>
